    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just drove off the lot for the first time! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept tucked away safely in the garage. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for the best of the best, this is definitely the one for you! Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
