    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the S54-powered legend. Featuring the high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, this unit delivers a perfectly linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the rod bearings and double VANOS system have been proactively addressed with documented service history. The chassis is structurally pristine, featuring reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a completely stock suspension geometry with MacPherson struts and multi-link rear architecture. Finished in its original factory pigment with zero clear coat failure, this specimen retains its forged Style 67 alloys and a surgically clean undercarriage. No diagnostic codes, no fluid seepage, and absolute mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
